textAnnotations.description:
WITH ALLTHE
INDICTMENTS OF STATE
PoLTCIANS! WITH ALL
THE OUTRAGE AT SIATE
SPENDING AND BACKRooM
DEALS! Do Yau uNDERSTAND
WHY WERE
ANGRY?
THEN WHY 19
YOUR HAND SiLL
IN MY POCKET!
I WANT
TO GIVE
OUT SOME
RAISES
YeS.
ㄩ
PA
